1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
(The next day)

2
00:00:06,050 --> 00:00:08,840
Hinata, it's already noon.

3
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:10,340
Mmm...

4
00:00:19,190 --> 00:00:23,610
I haven't even brushed my teeth yet.

5
00:00:32,570 --> 00:00:35,870
Students and working adults
have such different values.

6
00:00:35,870 --> 00:00:38,910
Waiting up for someone is exhausting, too.

7
00:00:42,210 --> 00:00:45,250
Don't push yourself too hard.
Sorry for waking you up.

8
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:58,480
I'm off to study.

9
00:00:58,480 --> 00:00:59,930
Okay.

10
00:01:00,850 --> 00:01:04,440
Good luck.

11
00:01:14,490 --> 00:01:19,950
How is Mizuki?
Are you two brothers getting along?
